# Paste your Cookie header on the line below (one line only).
# How to get it while logged into AMS:
#   1. Open any AMS PDF in Chrome/Safari
#   2. Open DevTools (Cmd+Option+I) -> Network tab
#   3. Reload the page, click the .pdf request
#   4. Under Request Headers, copy the full "Cookie:" value
#   5. Paste below (without the word "Cookie:")
#
# Then: cp ams_cookies.txt.example ams_cookies.txt  (and edit)
# Run:  python scripts/scan_pdfs.py --cookies-file ams_cookies.txt --limit 10
